						<p>2.3<span class="sub-heading">Error Status.</span> Odessa will provide Customer with online access to Odessa’s Error ticketing system.</p>
						<p>2.4<span class="sub-heading">Escalation Process.</span> The table below describes Odessa’s internal notification / escalation procedure with respect to Severity Level 1 Errors and Severity Level 2 Errors. Timeframes are during Odessa Standard Business Hours. </p>
